r e l e a s e info
| '
They Breathe is a journey into the depths of a forest filled with water. '
' As you swim deeper, you will come to slowly understand a world where
nothing is as it first seems, and where everyone is after the same
` precious resource oxygen!
`
` We don't want to get in the way of your exploration, so we leave most of
this game up to you to figure out on your own, from the controls to the: grand meaning of it all. So far our critics have all agreed on one
| thing: this is quite possibly the strangest thing you'll play this year
|
| Features: |
| Surreal atmosphere
| No hand-holding
| Hand-drawn HD art
| A story told through gameplay
| "Making of" feature
|: | More info: http://www.theworkingparts.com/theybreathe |
